{"tid":779854,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半好多時候講完就算","createTime":"2018-08-14T16:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T17:35:00.000Z","uid":62502,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"935df41ce00d4127f93beb9bf5845eccb016c28e","tid":779854,"uid":62502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:49:28.000Z","msg":"大事也好，小事也好，經常講完唔做/唔改變。唔知係我太認真記性好，定係佢大頭蝦，無論佢講幾鎖碎的事，我都會記入腦上心。<br />\n以前佢講好簡單的i love you已經夠我開心成日，但係唔知幾時開始，我覺得佢成日講完就算，無論佢講的說話幾好聽，我都唔再好似以前咁。<br />\n係咪因為我對佢無晒期望先咁，定係我個人衰，唔識知足？到底我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25d2fd4c4bde7d7f0d85763f0ff3d87fce6588d","tid":779854,"uid":62502,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:59:53.000Z","msg":"全能的連登仔可唔可以教我點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc1abbfed1203ac7d2ce8f66bb47a0965100724","tid":779854,"uid":147502,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:13:57.000Z","msg":"想問吓<br />\n你係咪藍絲"},{"pid":"0adbfb8c13d32d8990fdcc5d106e2580b172c77c","tid":779854,"uid":62502,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問吓<br />\n你係咪藍絲</blockquote><br />\n重要？"},{"pid":"6f3db8bbd63b6d22b1437a6def4ce0d48fe6ae81","tid":779854,"uid":15650,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"我明呀 同一個問題已經提出過好多次 但佢次次都係咁 真係講到口臭"},{"pid":"535b8bd69abfdab713df0fae80ab28e1db57e99b","tid":779854,"uid":62502,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明呀 同一個問題已經提出過好多次 但佢次次都係咁 真係講到口臭</blockquote><br />\n咁你之後點做？"},{"pid":"d46555d570ed41325d3e1461594db3ead97597ae","tid":779854,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0adbfb8c13d32d8990fdcc5d106e2580b172c77c","tid":779854,"uid":62502,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問吓<br />\n你係咪